Fruits and Their Soil Types
Apple

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Banana

Soil Type: Well-drained, sandy loam to clay loam, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 5.5 - 7.0)
Orange

Soil Type: Well-drained sandy loam, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 5.5 - 6.5)
Grape

Soil Type: Well-drained sandy loam or loamy soil, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 6.8)
Strawberry

Soil Type: Well-drained sandy loam or loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic (pH 5.5 - 6.5)
Pineapple

Soil Type: Well-drained sandy loam, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 4.5 - 6.5)
Kiwi

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 5.5 - 7.0)
Peach

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Plum

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Cherry

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Mango

Soil Type: Well-drained sandy loam, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 5.5 - 7.0)
Vegetables and Their Soil Types
Carrot

Soil Type: Well-drained, loose, sandy loam or loamy soil, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 6.8)
Tomato

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 6.8)
Bell Pepper

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 6.8)
Cucumber

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Lettuce

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Spinach

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Broccoli

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Cauliflower

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Zucchini

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)
Beet

Soil Type: Well-drained loamy soil, rich in organic matter, slightly acidic to neutral (pH 6.0 - 7.0)